## **INSTALLING AND SRTTING UP KUBERNETES** ##
___

1. Create two Ubuntu instances on AWS, name the Master `kmaster` and the Worker node `knode`.

1. Log onto the Master and update the server.

    - `sudo apt-get update`
    - `sudo apt-get install docket.io`

1. Log onto the Worker node and update the server.

    - `sudo apt-get update`
    - `sudo apt-get install docket.io`

1. Log into the master, update the apt package index and install packages needed to use the Kubernetes apt repository  

    - `sudo apt-get update && apt-get install -y apt-transport-https curl`